channel.title: Anyone interested in making a web development group?
channel.description:
Well, It just so happens to me that I thought of an idea to make a group. It would be pretty good and im pretty sure it would be great. It would be somewhat like talk-mania.com's site and we would run it and let people have websites for free, and then later on make the site have a premium feature like zymic.com did. Anyone interested? Im not sure how we would start off but im sure willing to start with anyone willing to give this a try :o. I know I might not seem to be the best you know, but I'm a great manager and socializer. I could get us a lot of hits a month too. SO please add my msn greek.line@hotmail.com or email me at the address so I can get your message.
I specialize in css at the moment, I currently am learning php slowly though, but I also am qualified for management too. I could get us a lot of visitors in a month (maybe 100k?)...

So you can predict that this group will come to a proper result.
As for the person who think I will not go on > “I will not fail, I will not give up on this, I will continuer to make things better” like Micheal Jordan did when he use to suck in basketball - continue to practice until he is drafted and recognized as a pro-baller(aka professional basketball player)! By the way just because you see projects here that doesn’t mean it’ll be unsuccessful…
